reviewText:
I wasn't interested in the story of lady o at all. Only reason to purchase with it was Paola Corazzi who is former Miss Roma and co-star in this film.
So,I've been satisfied 100%!  She is Perfect in it!!!

The advertising for this dvd and the dvd itself have nothing in common.  The picture on the cover of the dvd never appears in the video.  The verbage on the cover of the dvd has nothing to do with this movie.  The title on the cover of the dvd is an attempt to associate this dvd with "The Story of O" when this dvd has nothing to do with it or anything similar to it.  I doubt that "The Untold Story of the Lady O" was even the original title of this Italian soft porn movie - it looks like it was inserted into the video afterwards.
